<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>AI Dev Job Ad</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      background: #0f1117;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    .card {
      background: #1a1d27;
      border: 1px solid #2a2d3a;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 520px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    }

    .card-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    .icon-badge {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      min-width: 44px;
      background: #12131c;
      border: 1px solid #2a2d3a;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f0f1f5;
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .card-rate {
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #a78bfa;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .divider {
      height: 1px;
      background: #2a2d3a;
      margin: 1.1rem 0;
    }

    .intro {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9aa0b4;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #5a607a;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .list {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .list li {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #c8ccdc;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .list li::before {
      content: '';
      width: 5px;
      height: 5px;
      min-width: 5px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #a78bfa;
    }

    .perks-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .perk {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .badge {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 3px 9px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .badge-green  { background: #0d2e1a; color: #3ecf8e; }
    .badge-blue   { background: #0d1e3a; color: #4f9cf9; }
    .badge-purple { background: #1a1030; color: #a78bfa; }
    .badge-amber  { background: #2a1a00; color: #f59e0b; }

    .perk-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #c8ccdc;
    }

    .two-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 420px) {
      .two-cols {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 1rem;
      }
    }

    .stack-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 7px;
    }

    .stack-pill {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 4px 10px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      background: #1a1030;
      color: #a78bfa;
      border: 1px solid #2e1f55;
    }

    .cta-block {
      background: #12131c;
      border: 1px solid #2a2d3a;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    }

    .cta-text {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9aa0b4;
      line-height: 1.5;
      min-width: 0;
      word-break: break-all;
    }

    .cta-text strong {
      color: #f0f1f5;
      display: block;
      font-size: 13px;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
      word-break: normal;
    }

    .apply-btn {
      background: #a78bfa;
      color: #0f1117;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 9px 18px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 5px;
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 360px) {
      .apply-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    }

    .referral {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #5a607a;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .referral span { color: #3ecf8e; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="card">

  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="icon-badge">🚀</div>
    <div>
      <div class="card-title">We're Hiring: Software Engineer — AI Evaluation</div>
      <div class="card-rate">$40–$80/hr &nbsp;·&nbsp; Fully Remote &nbsp;·&nbsp; Flexible</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="intro">Exciting opportunity for JS/TS/Python/React developers!</p>
  <p class="intro" style="margin-top:6px;">We're hiring Software Engineers for AI Evaluation work — remote, flexible, and well-paid ($40–$80/hr).</p>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div>
    <div class="section-label">What you'll do</div>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Evaluate and improve AI model outputs</li>
      <li>Work with cutting-edge AI systems</li>
      <li>Flexible hours — great for freelancers or side work</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div>
    <div class="section-label">Tech stack</div>
    <div class="stack-row">
      <span class="stack-pill">JavaScript</span>
      <span class="stack-pill">TypeScript</span>
      <span class="stack-pill">Python</span>
      <span class="stack-pill">React</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="cta-block">
    <div class="cta-text">
      <strong>Ready to apply?</strong>
      tinyurl.com/ai-dev-job
    </div>
    <a href="https://tinyurl.com/ai-dev-job" class="apply-btn" target="_blank">Apply now ↗</a>
  </div>

  <div class="referral"><span>♦</span>&nbsp; Referrals welcome — feel free to share!</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
